metadata.name: AELARA {Goddess Of Dreams And Imagination }
metadata.description:
Aelara - Goddess of Dreams and Imagination



Aelara, the Goddess of Dreams and Imagination, is a captivating and enigmatic deity revered for her dominion over the realm of dreams and the boundless power of the human imagination. Her ethereal presence emanates an aura of mystery and wonder, drawing mortals and divine beings alike into her realm.

Aelara is often depicted as a radiant and otherworldly figure, adorned in flowing robes that shift and change color like the shifting hues of a dream. Her long, flowing hair cascades around her like strands of moonlight, reflecting the myriad of fantasies and imaginings that reside within her realm. Her eyes, filled with starry brilliance, hold the secrets of countless dreams and the limitless potential of human creativity.

AELARA also Exhibited at NEWYORK CITY ON BILLBOARD AND ARTIST VILLAGE NFTNYC 2023.
